<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redemption Request Approved</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #138808 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .success-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4edda 0%, #c3e6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #138808;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .success-box::before {
            content: "‚úÖ";
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #138808;
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .deal-summary {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .deal-title {
            color: #138808;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .business-name {
            color: #FF9933;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .detail-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(19, 136, 8, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #138808;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .qr-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px dashed #138808;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .qr-code {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #138808;
        }
        
        .instructions {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .instructions h4 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .instructions ol {
            color: #666;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .detail-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="success-icon">üéâ</div>
            <h1>Redemption Approved!</h1>
            <p>Your request has been accepted</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </p>
            
            <div class="success-box">
                <h2 style="color: #138808; margin-bottom: 15px;">Great News!</h2>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">
                    Your redemption request has been approved and is ready to use!
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="deal-summary">
                <h3 class="deal-title">{{dealTitle}}</h3>
                <p class="business-name">üìç {{businessName}}</p>
                
                <div class="detail-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Status</div>
                        <div class="detail-value" style="color: #138808;">Approved</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Redemption Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{redemptionDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Business</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{businessName}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <h4>üìã How to Use Your Approved Redemption:</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Visit {{businessName}} during their business hours</li>
                    <li>Show your membership card to the staff/cashier</li>
                    <li>They will scan or verify your membership card</li>
                    <li>Enjoy your savings and discount!</li>
                    <li>Don't forget to rate your experience</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #FF9933;">
                <h4 style="color: #FF9933; margin-bottom: 15px;">üí° Important Notes:</h4>
                <ul style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>This redemption is valid for one-time use only</li>
                    <li>Please check the deal's terms and conditions</li>
                    <li>Contact the business directly if you have any issues</li>
                    <li>Save this email as proof of your approved redemption</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;">Need help or have questions?</p>
                <p style="color: #138808; font-weight: bold;">
                    üìß support@indiansinghana.com<br>
                    üì± WhatsApp: +233 XXX XXX XXX
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>Thank you for supporting local Indian businesses!</p>
            <p>Email: support@indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
